### 2.6 School 4
POST {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolId": {{school4}},
  "nameOfInstitution": "DMS-1074 School 4",
  "educationOrganizationCategories": [
    { "educationOrganizationCategoryDescriptor": "uri://ed-fi.org/EducationOrganizationCategoryDescriptor#DMS-1074 School" }
  ],
