### 2.8 Class period with a boolean query field
POST {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/classPeriods
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolReference": {
    "schoolId": {{school1}}
  },
  "classPeriodName": "DMS-1074 Class Period",
  "officialAttendancePeriod": true
}

### 2.9 Student 1 with a date query field
POST {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/students
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUniqueId": "{{student1}}",
  "birthDate": "2010-01-13",
  "firstName": "DMS1074",
  "lastSurname": "StudentOne"
}

### 2.10 Student 2 with a date query field
POST {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/students
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentUniqueId": "{{student2}}",
  "birthDate": "2011-02-14",
  "firstName": "DMS1074",
  "lastSurname": "StudentTwo"
}

### 2.11 Student-school association for composite/reference filter coverage
POST {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/studentSchoolAssociations
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentReference": {
    "studentUniqueId": "{{student1}}"
  },
  "schoolReference": {
    "schoolId": {{school1}}
  },
  "entryGradeLevelDescriptor": "uri://ed-fi.org/GradeLevelDescriptor#DMS-1074 Grade",
  "entryDate": "2024-08-01"
}

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. Happy-path collection query checks
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 3.1 Baseline schools query - expect 200 and seeded schools in deterministic ID order
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?schoolId={{school1}}&totalCount=true
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.2 Paging: valid offset and limit - expect schools 4 and 5 in the page
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?offset=3&limit=2
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.3 Paging: offset greater than total - expect 200 and []
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?offset=600&limit=5
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.4 Paging: offset without limit - expect 200; skips the first four rows in collection order
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?offset=4
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.5 Property filter + limit - expect only DMS-1074 School 5
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?nameOfInstitution=DMS-1074+School+5&limit=2
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.6 Numeric property filter - expect school 3
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?schoolId={{school3}}
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.7 Descriptor endpoint filter - expect DMS-1074 Grade descriptor
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/gradeLevelDescriptors?codeValue=DMS-1074+Grade&totalCount=true
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.8 Boolean property filter - expect DMS-1074 Class Period
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/classPeriods?officialAttendancePeriod=true
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.9 Date property filter - expect Student 1
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/students?birthDate=2010-01-13
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 3.10 Reference/composite resource filter with paging - expect association for Student 1
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/studentSchoolAssociations?studentUniqueId={{student1}}&offset=0&limit=10
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. totalCount header checks
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 4.1 No matches with totalCount=true - expect Total-Count: 0
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?totalCount=true&nameOfInstitution=does+not+exist
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 4.2 totalCount=false - expect no Total-Count header
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?totalCount=false
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 4.3 totalCount omitted - expect no Total-Count header
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 4.4 totalCount=true with limit - expect page shorter than Total-Count
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?totalCount=true&limit=2
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. Case-insensitive query parameter checks
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 5.1 Case-insensitive resource query field name - expect DMS-1074 Class Period
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/classPeriods?CLaSSperIODName=DMS-1074+Class+Period
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 5.2 Case-insensitive LIMIT parameter - expect one school
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?liMIt=1
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 5.3 Case-insensitive OFFSET parameter - expect 200; skips the first school
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?OfFSeT=1&limit=1
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 5.4 Case-insensitive TOTALCOUNT parameter/value - expect Total-Count header
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?tOtAlCoUnT=trUE&limit=1
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. Validation failures
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 6.1 Invalid offset: negative - expect 400
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?offset=-1
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.2 Invalid offset: SQL-style payload - expect 400
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?offset=5%3B%20select%20*%20from%20users
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.3 Invalid limit: negative - expect 400
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?offset=0&limit=-1
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.4 Invalid limit: greater than maximum page size - expect 400
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?offset=0&limit=900
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.5 Invalid totalCount value - expect 400
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?totalCount=100
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.6 Invalid query field for resource - expect 400
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?invalidSchoolId={{school1}}
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.7 Invalid numeric query value - expect 400 data validation failure
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/schools?schoolId=not-a-number
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.8 Invalid boolean query value - expect 400 data validation failure
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/classPeriods?officialAttendancePeriod=not-a-boolean
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}

### 6.9 Invalid date query value - expect 400 data validation failure
GET {{dataApi}}/ed-fi/students?birthDate=not-a-date
Authorization: bearer {{dmsToken}}
